ily]] |accessdate=2 April 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191012092237/https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/a/201909/14/WS5d8094dba310cf3e3556bf83.html |archivedate=October 12, 2019 |date=September 14, 2019}}</ref> such as [[GQ Style]],<ref>{{cite news |title=\u674e\u73b0\u89e3\u9501\u5168\u65b0\u5c01\u9762 \u8d85\u5f3a\u53ef\u5851\u6027\u6f14\u7ece\u8d28\u611f\u9ed1\u767d\u5927\u7247 - \u4e2d\u56fd\u5a31\u4e50\u7f51 |url=http://pic.yule.com.cn/8849/ |accessdate=April 12, 2020 |work=China Entertainment Network |date=September 25, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191003094712/http://pic.yule.com.cn/8849/ |archivedate=October 3, 2019}}</ref>\n\n===Weibo===\nLi likes to share about sports, book lists, music and movies on his\n[[Microblogging in China|Weibo]]. In 2019, during the broadcast of his drama ''Go Go Squid'', Li Xian's [[Baidu]] Index, [[WeChat]] Index and Weibo all rank first in terms of follower growth.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Syntesis |first1=Strait Network |title=What is Li Xian \u2019s boyfriend in July, and why is Li Xian \u2019s boyfriend in July? |script-title=zh:\u674e\u73b0 \u4e03\u6708\u7537\u53cb\u4ec0\u4e48\u6897\uff0c\u674e\u73b0\u4e3a\u4ec0\u4e48\u662f\u4e03\u6708\u7537\u53cb\uff1f|url=http://m.hxnews.com/news/yl/ylxw/201907/17/1778378.shtml |website=hexanews.com | date=July 17, 2019 |accessdate= April 5, 2020 |language =zh}}</ref> \nHis followers on Weibo grew quickly from 5 million to 20 million.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Transcribers |first1=Motley Fool |title=Weibo Corporation (WB) Q3 2019 Earnings Call Transcript |url=https://www.fool.com/earnings/call-transcripts/2019/11/14/weibo-corporation-wb-q3-2019-earnings-call-transcr.aspx |website=The Motley Fool |accessdate=2 April 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191115015810/https://www.fool.com/earnings/call-transcripts/2019/11/14/weibo-corporation-wb-q3-2019-earnings-call-transcr.aspx |archivedate=November 15, 2019 |language=en |date=November 14, 2019 |quote=This q