n poses for fashion magazine - Chinadaily.com.cn |url=https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/a/201909/14/WS5d8094dba310cf3e3556bf83.html |website=[[China Daily]] |accessdate=2 April 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191012092237/https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/a/201909/14/WS5d8094dba310cf3e3556bf83.html |archivedate=October 12, 2019 |date=September 14, 2019}}</ref> such as [[GQ Style]],<ref>{{cite news |title=\u674e\u73b0\u89e3\u9501\u5168\u65b0\u5c01\u9762 \u8d85\u5f3a\u53ef\u5851\u6027\u6f14\u7ece\u8d28\u611f\u9ed1\u767d\u5927\u7247 - \u4e2d\u56fd\u5a31\u4e50\u7f51 |url=http://pic.yule.com.cn/8849/ |accessdate=April 12, 2020 |work=China Entertainment Network |date=September 25, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191003094712/http://pic.yule.com.cn/8849/ |archivedate=October 3, 2019}}</ref>\n\n===Weibo===\nLi likes to share about sports, book lists, music and movies on his\n[[Microblogging in China|Weibo]]. In 2019, during the broadcast of his drama ''Go Go Squid'', Li Xian's [[Baidu]] Index, [[WeChat]] Index and Weibo all rank first in terms of follower growth.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Syntesis |first1=Strait Network |title=What is Li Xian \u2019s boyfriend in July, and why is Li Xian \u2019s boyfriend in July? |script-title=zh:\u674e\u73b0 \u4e03\u6708\u7537\u53cb\u4ec0\u4e48\u6897\uff0c\u674e\u73b0\u4e3a\u4ec0\u4e48\u662f\u4e03\u6708\u7537\u53cb\uff1f|url=http://m.hxnews.com/news/yl/ylxw/201907/17/1778378.shtml |website=hexanews.com | date=July 17, 2019 |accessdate= April 5, 2020 |language =zh}}</ref> \nHis followers on Weibo grew quickly from 5 million to 20 million.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Transcribers |first1=Motley Fool |title=Weibo Corporation (WB) Q3 2019 Earnings Call Transcript |url=https://www.fool.com/earnings/call-transcripts/2019/11/14/weibo-corporation-wb-q3-2019-earnings-call-transcr.aspx |website=The Motley Fool |accessdate=2 April 2020 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191115015810/https://www.fool.com/earnings/call-transcripts/2019/11/14/weibo-corporation-wb-q3-2019-earnings-call-transcr.aspx |archivedate=November 15, 2019 |language=en |date=November 14, 2019 |quote=This quarter a TV series called Go Go Squid! became very popular on Weibo as well as its leading actor Li Xian whose fan base grew quickly from 5 million to 20 million.}}</ref>\n\n==Endorsements==\nLi is the ambassador of [[China Youth Development Foundation]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=TV |first1=London |title=Chinese Actor Li Xian and His Fans Playing an Unexpected Role against the Coronavirus |url=https://london-tv.co.uk/chinese-actor-li-xian-and-his-fans-playing-an-unexpected-role-against-the-coronavirus/ |website=London TV |accessdate=2 April 2020 |date=31 January 2020}}</ref>\nIn 2019 Li appointed as the global spokers person of [[Honor (brand)|Honor]],<ref>{{cite web |last1=Yordari |title=Honor 30 and 30 Pro arriving on April 15 |url=https://www.gsmarena.com/honor_30_series_officially_arriving_on_april_15-news-42343.php |website=GSMArena.com |accessdate=1 April 2020 |language=en |date=March 31, 2020}}</ref> the first brand ambassador of [[Atlantis Resorts|Atlantis Sanya]],<ref>{{cite web |last1=Sanya |first1=Atlantis |title=Official Announcement! \"July Boyfriend\" Li Xian Officially Appointed As Brand Ambassador For Atlantis Sanya |url=https://www.accesswire.com/559785/Official-Announcement-July-Boyfriend-Li-Xian-Officially-Appointed-As-Brand-Ambassador-For-Atlantis-Sanya |website=www.accesswire.com/ |accessdate=1 April 2020 |date=September 16, 2019 |quote=Atlantis Sanya officially announced actor Li Xian as the resort\u2019s first Brand Ambassador}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Atlantis Sanya Invited Li Xian to be its Brand Ambassador |url=https://www.accesswire.com/564055/Atlantis-Sanya-Invited-Li-Xian-to-be-its-Brand-Ambassador |website=www.accesswire.com |accessdate=1 April 2020 |language=en |date=October 24, 2020}}</ref> and Av\u00e8ne (in 15 years). In the same year he appointed as brand ambassador of [[Est\u00e9e Lauder Companies|Est\u00e9e Lauder]],<ref>{{cite web |last1=Lavin |first1=Frank |title=How Does 12.12 Fit Into Your China Strategy? |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/franklavin/2019/12/12/how-does-1212-fit-into-your-china-strategy/#55fb1e6f3121 |website=Forbes |accessdate=1 April 2020 |language=en |date=December 12, 2019 |quote=Estee Lauder, as an example, produced an ad campaign using celebrities Li Xian and Yang Mi to promote its Aqua Brilliance line.}}</ref>, [[PUMA]], [[Levi Strauss & Co.|Levi's]], [[Yili Group|Yili]], [[Midea Group#Products|Midea]], [[JD.com]], [[Lay's]], two beverage company, and an ice cream brand.{{Citation needed|date=April 2020}}\n\n==Filmography==\n{{Main|Li Xian filmography}}\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n;Film\n* ''[[Schemes in Antiques]]'' (2020) as Yao Buran\n* ''[[Red Fox Scholar]]'' (2020) as Bao Shisan\n* ''[[Leap (film)|Leap]]'' (2020, cameo)\n* ''[[The Enigma of Arrival (film)|The Enigma of Arrival]]'' (2020) as Xiao Long\n* ''[[Love Song 1980]]'' (2020) as Zheng Wen\n* ''[[The Captain (2019 film)|The Captain]]'' (2019, cameo)\n* ''[[Nuts (2018 film)|Nuts]] '' (2018) as Xu Zicong\n* ''[[The Founding of an Army]]'' (2017) as Luo Ruohang\n* ''[[Deadly Love]]'' (2017) as Fang Zhibin\n* ''[[Love O2O (film)|Love O2O]]'' (2016) as Yu Banshan\n* ''[[Who Sleeps My Bro]]'' (2016) as Xie Xun\n* ''[[Singing When We're Young]]'' (2013) as Da Wei\n* ''[[Feng Shui (2012 film)|Feng Shui]]'' (2012) as Ma Xiaobao\n\n{{col-2}}\n;Television\n* ''[[A Love Never Lost]]'' (2020)\n* ''[[Sword Dynasty]]'' (2019) as Ding Ning\n* ''[[Go Go Squid!]]'' (2019) as Han Shangyan\n* ''[[Women in Shanghai]]'' (2018) as Chen Xiaowei \n* ''[[Only Side by Side with You]]'' (2018) as Cheng Jianxiong\n* ''[[Tientsin Mystic]]'' (2017) as Guo Deyou\n* ''[[Rush to the Dead Summer (TV series)|Rush to the Dead Summer]]'' (2017) as Qing Yun (Cameo)\n* ''[[Medical Examiner Dr. Qin]]'' (2016) as Lin Tao\n* ''[[Who Sleeps My Bro]]'' (2016) as Xie Xun\n* ''[[Four Ladies (TV series)|Four Ladies]]'' (2016) as Ding Zihui\n* ''[[City of Fantasy]]'' (2014) as Ah Liang\n{{col-end}}\n\n===Others===\n====Short film====\n{| class=\"wikitable\" \n|-\n! width=10|Year\n! English title\n! Chinese title \n! Role\n! Notes/Ref.\n|- \n| rowspan=2|2013 ||''12 Years'' || {{lang|zh|12\u5e74}} || Lin Xiaofeng || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.17173.com/content/2013-07-22/20130722155531452_all.shtml|script-title=zh:\u300a12\u5e74\u300b\u5fae\u7535\u5f71 \u4e00\u5982\u521d\u89c1\u76f8\u4f34\u6c38\u8fdc|date=July 22, 2013|language=zh}}</ref> \n|- \n|''Confess'' || {{lang|zh|\u8868\u767d}} || || \n|- \n|2016 || ''The Gift'' || {{lang|zh-Hans|\u661f\u9645\u793c\u7269}} || Wang Qi || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.yule.com.cn/html/201603/215328.html|script-title=zh:\u674e\u73b0\u79d1\u5e7b\u5fae\u7535\u5f71\u53d1\u5e03 \u6f14\u7ece\u661f\u9645\u7a7f\u8d8a\u4e4b\u7231|date=March 12, 2016|website=Yule|language=zh}}</ref>\n|- \n| 2018 || ''Explore Melbourne with Li Xian'' || {{lang|zh-Hans|\u58a8\u5c14\u672c \u6211\u672c\u7279\u7acb\u72ec\u884c}} ||  || Promotional film for Visit Victoria Campaign Launch Event |<ref>{{cite web|url=http://travel.sina.com.cn/outbound/news/2018-03-13/detail-ifyscsmv1764467.shtml|script-title=zh:\u7ef4\u591a\u5229\u4e9a\u5dde\u65c5\u6e38\u5c40\u53d1\u5e03\u4e2d\u56fd\u533a\u54c1\u724c\uff1a\u58a8\u5c14\u672c\uff0c\u6211\u672c\u7279\u7acb\u72ec\u884c|date=March 13, 2019|website=Sina|language=zh}}</ref>\n|- \n|}\n\n====Music video====\n{| class=\"wikitable\" \n|-\n! width=10|Year\n! English title\n! Chinese title \n! Singer\n! Notes/Ref.\n|- \n| 2013 || \"Singing When We Are Young\" || {{lang|zh-Hans|\u521d\u604b\u672a\u6ee1}} || [[Zhang Hanyun]] & Cao Xuanbin ||\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2015 || \"I Am Jiang Xiaobai\" || {{lang|zh|\u6211\u662f\u6c5f\u5c0f\u767d}} || Zhang Qi || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.163.com/16/0328/17/BJ8TM19A00032PQV.html|script-title=zh:\u674e\u73b0\u7a0b\u781a\u79cb\u9648\u8bfa\u8d70\u7ea2 \u300a\u6211\u662f\u6c5f\u5c0f\u76